Small, secretive local cabals of merchants are everywhere in the Realms, and seemingly always have been. One of the most successful, in a city infamous for its cabals, is "The [[Silent Sail]]" of [[Marsember]]. {{Dusup|185/Eye on the Realms: Silent Sail}}
